  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study was designed to find the optimum AVN944 dose to use in combination with gemcitabine
      in patients with pancreatic cancer and see if the combination of the 2 drugs was more
      effective for treating pancreatic cancer than using gemcitabine alone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
